{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not as a teacher, but she had formal training, as such.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she tried to teach me how to read and write in Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember writing, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't remember-- and I didn't have any books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were no books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I drew pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Houses, mostly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And therefore, they thought that when I would grow up, I would become an engineer-- an architect, actually, because I drew lots of houses, for some reason.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For four years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From 1939, so it must have-- I think it was the 1st of September.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just read the other day that the war-- that Hitler came to Poland from the 1st of September, 1939 til 1943.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do remember some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing that remind-- that I remember very distinctly was the main topic of conversation, [DRINKS] apart from survival, was the Messiah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even as a young child at that age, I remember that they believed that the Messiah was miraculously going to come out of the heavens, whisk them out of this little ghetto, and-- and free them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody believed this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was sort of instilled in me, and I thought about-- and I-- I imagined what this Messiah was going to be like.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the Messiah very well-- I suppose this was not unusual for people to believe in such a thing-- that it would-- he would actually come and rescue you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was no-- the feeling was that there was no way of being rescued.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was one time, actually where-- my father recounted, and I remember this well, because he said that they came and they said that if you have any relatives outside of Poland, they would be-- we would be deported to that country.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
